{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-with-the-strict-inequality-operator","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Poredjenje sa Strogim Operatorom Nejednakosti","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Operator stroge nejednakosti (<code>!==</code>) je logicka suprotnost operatoru stroge jednakosti. Znaci \"nije tacno jednako\" i vraca <code>false</code> tamo gde bi operator stroge jednakosti vratio <code>true</code>, i obrnuto. Operator stroge nejednakosti ne konvertuje tipove podataka.</p>\n<p><strong>Primeri</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">3 !==  3  // false\n3 !== '3' // true\n4 !==  3  // true\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244d3","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Dodajte operator stroge nejednakosti u <code>if</code> izraz tako da funkcija vraca string <code>Not Equal</code> kada <code>val</code> nije striktno jednako <code>17</code></p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16791,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-with-the-strict-inequality-operator"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"// Setup\nfunction testStrictNotEqual(val) {\n  if (val) { // Change this line\n    return \"Not Equal\";\n  }\n  return \"Equal\";\n}\n\ntestStrictNotEqual(10);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>testStrictNotEqual(17)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Equal</code></p>","testString":"assert(testStrictNotEqual(17) === 'Equal');"},{"text":"<p><code>testStrictNotEqual(\"17\")</code> treba da vrati string <code>Not Equal</code></p>","testString":"assert(testStrictNotEqual('17') === 'Not Equal');"},{"text":"<p><code>testStrictNotEqual(12)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Not Equal</code></p>","testString":"assert(testStrictNotEqual(12) === 'Not Equal');"},{"text":"<p><code>testStrictNotEqual(\"bob\")</code> treba da vrati string <code>Not Equal</code></p>","testString":"assert(testStrictNotEqual('bob') === 'Not Equal');"},{"text":"<p>Treba da koristite operator <code>!==</code></p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/(val\\s*!==\\s*\\d+)|(\\d+\\s*!==\\s*val)/g).length > 0);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"comparison-with-the-strict-inequality-operator","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-with-the-greater-than-operator","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-with-the-inequality-operator","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244d3","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-